Civora — Licensing Overview
===========================

Civora is a multi-licensed project. Different parts of this repository are
released under different licenses so that the shared universe stays open and
player-governed, tools and modules stay easy to build, creative assets stay
free to share, and the Civora name and logo stay protected.

This file is a human-readable summary. The authoritative, path-by-path mapping
is in COPYRIGHT.md, and the full, verbatim license texts are in the LICENSES/
directory. Machine-readable licensing is declared in REUSE.toml following the
REUSE specification (https://reuse.software).

Primary license
---------------
The Civora client, the Reality Kernel, and the core protocol crates — the
software you run and distribute — are licensed under the GNU Affero General
Public License, version 3 or (at your option) any later version.

    SPDX-License-Identifier: AGPL-3.0-or-later
    Full text: LICENSES/AGPL-3.0-or-later.txt

Because Civora is peer-to-peer and network-served, the AGPL is used
deliberately: anyone who runs a modified Civora node for other players must
offer those users the corresponding source. This keeps the universe forkable
and auditable.

Other components
----------------
  - SDK (sdk/**): Apache License 2.0 — permissive, so anyone can build modules,
    tools, and integrations without copyleft obligations.
        SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0
        Full text: LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt

  - Official assets (assets/official/**) and Genesis Realm assets
    (realms/genesis-realm/assets/**): Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike
    4.0 International.
        SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-SA-4.0
        Full text: LICENSES/CC-BY-SA-4.0.txt

  - Realm templates (realms/templates/**): your choice of Apache License 2.0
    OR Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International — maximally reusable
    starting points for code and content.
        SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0 OR CC-BY-4.0
        Full texts: LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt, LICENSES/CC-BY-4.0.txt

  - Civora name and logo (assets/logo/**, civora_logo.svg, logo_concept.png):
    trademark-protected. NOT covered by the licenses above and not freely
    relicensed.
        SPDX-License-Identifier: LicenseRef-Civora-Trademark
        See: TRADEMARK.md, LICENSES/LicenseRef-Civora-Trademark.txt

Contributions
-------------
Unless stated otherwise, contributions are made under the license that already
applies to the file or directory you are changing (inbound = outbound). See
CONTRIBUTING.md.

